**Overview**

The dashboard offers a consolidated view of SentinelOne unified alerts for monitoring and investigation. Alerts over time highlights activity spikes and emerging alerts; bar charts of alerts break down by detection engine and threat classification. Pie charts show severity and confidence distribution. Top assets by highest alerts and top alerts by file hash are shown in tables, supporting identification of high-risk assets and the file hashes most frequently associated with alerts.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/sentinel_one/overview)
